CDP (Cisco Discovery Protocol) iyo LLDP (Link Layer Discovery Protocol) waa laba protocol oo loo adeegsado device discovery ‚Äì waxay kuu oggolaanayaan inaad ogaato qalabka ku xiran port-yada switch-kaaga (tusaale, router, switch, IP phone iwm).

‚úÖ 1. CDP (Cisco Proprietary)
üîß Enable/Disable CDP
CDP waa enabled by default.

‚ûï Enable CDP (Global):

Switch(config)# cdp run
‚ûñ Disable CDP (Global):

Switch(config)# no cdp run
Disable CDP per-interface:

Switch(config)# interface fa0/1
Switch(config-if)# no cdp enable
Enable CDP per-interface:

Switch(config)# interface fa0/1
Switch(config-if)# cdp enable
üîç View CDP Neighbors:

Switch# show cdp neighbors
Switch# show cdp neighbors detail
‚úÖ 2. LLDP (Standard Protocol - IEEE 802.1AB)
LLDP waxaa taageera Cisco, HP, Juniper, iwm. Waxaa laga yaabaa in aysan default uusan u shaqeynaynin Cisco devices (you must enable it).

üîß Enable/Disable LLDP
‚ûï Enable LLDP (Global):

Switch(config)# lldp run
‚ûñ Disable LLDP (Global):

Switch(config)# no lldp run
Enable/Disable LLDP per-interface:

Switch(config)# interface fa0/1
Switch(config-if)# lldp transmit
Switch(config-if)# lldp receive
üîç View LLDP Neighbors:

Switch# show lldp neighbors
Switch# show lldp neighbors detail
üß™ Tusaale Config Dhameystiran (CDP + LLDP)

Switch(config)# cdp run
Switch(config)# lldp run

Switch(config)# interface range fa0/1 - 2
Switch(config-if-range)# cdp enable
Switch(config-if-range)# lldp transmit
Switch(config-if-range)# lldp receive
